data.description: Entertainment-Ready Home with Desirable Updates and Central Location. Extraordinarily Charming Home with Brand-New Gourmet Kitchen! Ideally nestled in the highly coveted (top-ranked) Homewood Flossmoor High School District, this 4BR/3BA, 2,664sqft residence radiates welcoming warmth with an attractive exterior color scheme, a verdant 0.28-acre lot, and classic exterior brick accents. Fabulously illuminated with natural light, the lovingly maintained interior features gleaming wood floors, neutral paint hues, bright white trim, and a spacious living room with sliding glass doors to a party-perfect front deck. Catering to modern culinary needs, the uber-chic kitchen dazzles with stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, gas stove, dishwasher, built-in microwave, French door refrigerator, white shaker cabinetry, fashionable backsplash, and an adjoining dining room. Post-dinner beverages may be enjoyed in the adjacent family room, which has vaulted ceilings and sliding glass doors to the oversized deck. Designed for relaxation, the main-level primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and stylish en suite with a dual sink vanity. Two main-level bedrooms and a full bathroom with a shower/tub combo offer abundant comfort, while the lower-level affords multigenerational versatility with a large bedroom and a full bathroom with a stall shower. Other features: attached 2.5 car garage, laundry room with utility sink, quick 28-mile drive to Downtown Chicago, close to shopping, I-294, I-80, I-57, major retail stores such as Starbucks, Walgreens, Best Buy, Target, Jewel,  medical facilities, and parks, and so much more.   A must see!
